{"tid":1858126,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★星期一 A股復市　中證監多招維穩","createTime":"2020-02-02T13:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T14:58:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c0af03916216487ed069c57570e4809155806007","tid":1858126,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:42:19.000Z","msg":"對於開市後A股市場可能出現的異動，有關部門將保持高度警惕，堅持底線思維，出台和研究對沖工具，緩解市場恐慌情緒。<br />\n<br />\n此外，為做好特殊時期疫情防控工作，2月3日(周一)當晚起暫停期貨夜盤交易，具體的恢復時間另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n為疏解相關企業的流動性困難，防範違約風險，降低市場影響，中證監將採取相關措施。一方面，對疫情防控期間到期的公司債券，發行人生產經營正常的，會通過設立綠色通道等措施，支持發新還舊；另一方面督促受託管理人加強與投資者的溝通協調，積極引導投資者對疫情防控期間到期的公司債券，通過與發行人達成展期安排、調整還本付息周期等方式，幫助發行人渡過困難期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200202/bkn-20200202185157621-0202_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200202%2Fbkn-20200202185157621-0202_00842_001.html&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V5sm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=58b4f72d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200202/bkn-20200202185157621-0202_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"182ef1d760cf04ef6a209a28736f12919879d27d","tid":1858126,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9bca32a92d32bee595202194241f59e45f5594","tid":1858126,"uid":77196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"邊個沽空就送去武漢，肯定升到上外太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4966eec0369d8660c309a175dbbf945696e01480","tid":1858126,"uid":87977,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13: